title: De Oldify A Nile Cruise To Luxor In 1926 [ 1080p# S AI P 3] ( 1926)

sources.title: De Oldify A Nile Cruise To Luxor In 1926 [ 1080p# S AI P 3] ( 1926)
sources.description: Artificially colorized and restored interesting old film of a visit to Egypt including a cruise on the Nile by Holland America Line cruise passengers in 1926. The film also includes a visit to a camel market and to a horse racetrack. Very high quality! Please watch in full-HD. Source: BeeldEnGeluid).
